---
layout: base.njk
lang: en
title: "Build Hub"
description: "Build Hub — Project Management in Sicily. From design to delivery, your single point of contact for every project."
root: "../"
stats:
  - number: 50
    label: "Projects Completed"
  - number: 15
    label: "Years of Experience"
  - number: 100
    label: "Happy Clients"
permalink: "/en/index.html"
---

{% from "icons.njk" import serviceIcon %}

  <section class="hero hero-home">
    <div class="hero-glow"></div>
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1 class="hero-title">Build Hub</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">Project Management</p>
      <p class="hero-sub">From design to delivery, your single interlocutor in Sicily.</p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="contact.html" class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg">
          Request a consultation
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="18" height="18" stroke="currentColor" fill="none" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
        </a>
        <a href="services.html" class="btn btn-white btn-lg">
          Discover our services
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-wave"></div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title reveal">Our method</h2>
      <div class="metodo-grid reveal-stagger">
        <div class="metodo-card">
          <div class="metodo-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" fill="none" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M9.09 9a3 3 0 015.83 1c0 2-3 3-3 3"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Listen and analyse</h3>
          <p>We start from your needs. We analyse the context, the challenges and the opportunities of the project to set clear and shared goals.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="metodo-card">
          <div class="metodo-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" fill="none" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><line x1="16" y1="2" x2="16" y2="6"/><line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="6"/><line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"/><path d="M9 14l2 2 4-4"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Plan and coordinate</h3>
          <p>We define phases, timelines and costs. We bring together the right professionals and coordinate every activity with method and precision.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="metodo-card">
          <div class="metodo-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" fill="none" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/><polyline points="9 12 11 14 15 10"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Oversee and deliver</h3>
          <p>We monitor every phase of the project, ensuring quality of execution, compliance with deadlines and rigorous cost control.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-surface">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title reveal">Our services</h2>
      <div class="servizi-grid reveal-stagger">
        {% for s in collections.services_en %}
        <a href="services.html#{{ s.data.slug }}" class="servizio-card">
          <div class="servizio-icon">
            {{ serviceIcon(s.data.icon, "") }}
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>{{ s.data.title }}</h3>
            <p class="servizio-excerpt">{{ s.data.description | truncate(90, true, "...") }}</p>
            <span class="cta-link">
              Learn more
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" fill="none" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
            </span>
          </div>
        </a>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
      <div class="section-footer reveal" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 2.5rem;">
        <a href="services.html" class="btn btn-outline">All services</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="stats-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="stats-grid reveal-stagger">
        {% for stat in stats %}
        <div>
          <div class="stat-number" data-target="{{ stat.number }}">0</div>
          <p class="stat-label">{{ stat.label }}</p>
        </div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <div class="reveal" style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <h2 class="section-title" style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">Ready to start?</h2>
        <p style="color: rgba(10,10,10,0.6); font-size: 1.125rem; margin-bottom: 2.5rem;">Tell us about your project. We will get back to you with an initial analysis within 48 hours.</p>
        <a href="contact.html" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">
          Request a consultation
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="18" height="18" stroke="currentColor" fill="none" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="territorio-section">
    <div class="territorio-glow"></div>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="reveal">
        <div class="territorio-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 100 100" stroke="currentColor" fill="none" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M82.3 79.5L81.5 73.5L84.4 69.1L88.2 67.2L86.5 66.3L87.1 63.9L85.3 63.3L83.7 60.4L83.9 59.0L85.9 58.6L84.4 56.9L81.3 56.0L80.9 49.9L83.6 46.2L84.6 39.7L92.9 27.8L95.4 21.4L97.5 20.4L93.8 19.4L87.3 22.8L85.8 22.7L85.2 20.4L84.8 23.3L81.8 25.7L75.8 23.4L70.8 24.5L66.3 28.3L57.7 30.3L49.6 29.0L41.3 31.6L36.1 29.1L35.3 26.4L30.8 26.5L28.8 22.2L25.1 24.2L22.1 23.8L21.0 25.4L21.4 27.6L16.8 29.6L14.4 28.1L11.6 23.6L11.1 26.3L4.6 30.0L5.7 30.6L4.6 31.2L3.5 34.0L4.3 35.4L2.5 37.9L4.0 41.8L8.1 44.1L9.5 46.7L17.1 46.3L20.3 49.3L24.5 49.6L32.1 56.4L35.8 57.1L38.9 60.3L45.2 63.9L51.5 63.7L56.5 65.5L60.3 69.4L63.5 75.5L71.9 78.6L74.4 77.6L78.8 78.6L80.8 80.6L82.3 79.5Z"/></svg></div>
        <h2>Rooted in Sicily</h2>
        <p>We operate throughout Sicily with deep-rooted knowledge of local specificities, the regional regulatory framework and the best construction practices of the Mediterranean area.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
